text: Kazimierz Macioch (1 June 1932 - 26 March 2011) was a Polish wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:2011 deaths Category:Polish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Poland Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:People from Ostrów Mazowiecka County Category:Sportspeople from Masovian Voivodeship Category:People from Warsaw Voivodeship (1919–1939)
